headline: Why Is EMCOR (EME) Stock Soaring Today
summary: Shares of specialty construction contractor company EMCOR (NYSE:EME) jumped 7.8% in the afternoon session after peer, Comfort Systems, posted strong third-quarter 2025 results that surpassed analyst expectations on both revenue and profit, driven by a record backlog.
